summary: Several news organizations, including The New York Times, NPR, NBC Chicago, TIME, Axios, STAT, El Paso Times, and BBC.com, have released articles and updates regarding the first presidential debate between Joe Biden and Donald Trump for the 2024 election. Hillary Clinton, a former presidential candidate, shares her observations and expectations in an opinion piece for The New York Times.
